Today on your birthday all I have to say is that I miss you soo sooooooo much🥺……

Allah has blessed me with the best 4 sisters in the world and you are one of them just like my own blood♥️you are the  bestest sis in law that anyone can ask for😘#alhumdulillah 
…..
from friends to besties to sisters in law to soul sisters with whom i can do all my crazy things, some used to even call us ‘aajunum maajunum😅coz of the things we do together🙊

I pray to allah that may he make our bond even more stronger day by day and may it last forever❣️..
And may allah always keep you this  same hyper active, ..alwys the cheerfull girl,.. alwys the supportive & always the most talkative person around us😂

…it really hurts to think that we won’t be together in muscat like we used to be😓..

Cant wait to meet u soon & continue our craziness togther especially twinning blogging vlogging & reeling & many more❣️😍

Happy birthday day my dear & dnt forget you are getting old😛😘

latestIgtvVideos.title: My Girl Turns  4 years Today😍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.
.
.

March 10th, 2017 8 pm ,A beautiful baby and an awesome mom was born❣️
It's our angels 4th birthday and still am like it all happened yesterday 
I am still in Delivery trauma 😐I literally can’t get over the labor fear till now..!😥

 I am super proud of myself that I did my motherhood well  as looking back to our beautiful 4 years 
I have carried you within my body, I have slept you on my chest. wiped away tears and spent a sleepless night cradling you. But I wouldn’t have it any other way. There is no greater honor, love or blessings🥰 also am so proud of my baby we completed the beautiful 4years and we were there  to support each other, love, cute fights &all our sleepless nights, and what more  enjoyed every bit of our life😍 
Honestly, whenever I am down I used to talk to her and she consoles me and loves me more than anyone does... and I don’t know how many of them can relate to this...!
she is just 4 but mashallah the way she takes care of us is just speechless💕
Every child is beautiful and blessed in their own way...!

And these 4 years went so quickly. The struggle was real but quite enjoyed with this muchkin. And My dear baby, pappa, and mamma will be always there for you in your ups and downs❣️I wish you All the success happiness health wealth, and Imaan ❤️
Aameen ya rabb☺️

HAPPY BIRTHDAY MY ANGEL💕

PS- I made this small video clip to surprise her and I made her watch on the Tv. 
And Her reaction was priceless 🥰
.
.
